\c 4
\s UMozisi ulaya abantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuthi bagcine imilayo
\p
\v 1 Khathesi-ke, Israyeli, zwana izimiso lezahlulelo engilifundisa zona\x + Levi 18.4.\x*, ukuzenza, ukuze liphile, lingene lidle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo elinika lona.
\v 2 Kaliyikwengezelela elizwini engililaya lona, lingaphunguli \add lutho\add* kulo, ukuze ligcine imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu engililaya yona\x + 12.32. Zaga 30.6. Isam. 22.18,19. Josh. 1.7.\x*.
\v 3 Amehlo enu abonile iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakwenzayo ngenxa kaBhali-Peyori\x + Nani 23.28.\x*; ngoba wonke umuntu owalandela uBhali-Peyori, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu yambhubhisa phakathi kwenu;
\v 4 kodwa lina elanamathela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu liyaphila lonke lamuhla.
\v 5 Bonani, ngilifundisile izimiso lezahlulelo, njengokungilaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami, ukuthi lenze njalo phakathi kwelizwe eliya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo.
\v 6 Ngakho zigcineni, lizenze; ngoba lokhu kuyinhlakanipho yenu lokuqedisisa kwenu emehlweni ezizwe\x + Jobe 28.28. Hlab. 111.10. Zaga 1.7. 9.10.\x* ezizakuzwa zonke lezizimiso zithi: Isibili lesisizwe esikhulu singabantu abahlakaniphileyo labaqedisisayo\x + Gen. 20.11.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba yisiphi isizwe esikhulu\x + 2 Sam. 7.23.\x* esilabonkulunkulu abaseduze laso njengeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu ekumbizeni kwethu konke\x + Hlab. 145.18. 148.14. Hlab. 46.1.\x*?
\v 8 Futhi yisiphi isizwe esikhulu esilezimiso lezahlulelo ezilungileyo njengalumlayo wonke engiwubeka phambi kwenu lamuhla?
\s Ukukhunjulwa kwalokho okwenzakalayo eHorebe
\p
\v 9 Kuphela ziqaphele, ugcine kakhulu umphefumulo wakho, hlezi ukhohlwe izinto amehlo akho azibonileyo, njalo hlezi zisuke enhliziyweni yakho, zonke izinsuku zempilo yakho\x + Zaga 4.23.\x*. Njalo uzazise abantwana bakho labantwana babantwana bakho\x + Gen. 18.19. Dute. 6.7. 11.19. Hlab. 78.4-6. Efe. 6.4.\x*,
\v 10 \add ukuthi\add* ngosuku owema ngalo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eHorebe\x + Eks. 19.9,16. Heb. 12.18,19.\x*, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kimi: Ngibuthanisela abantu ngibe sengibazwisa amazwi ami, ukuze bafunde ukungesaba zonke izinsuku abazaziphila emhlabeni, bafundise njalo abantwana babo.
\v 11 Laselisondela, lema ngaphansi kwentaba, lentaba yayivutha umlilo kwaze kwaba phakathi kwamazulu\x + Eks. 19.18. 20.18. Dute. 5.22,23.\x*, \add lo\add*mnyama, amayezi, lomnyama onzima.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kini iphakathi komlilo\x + 5.4,22.\x*; lezwa ilizwi lamazwi, kodwa kalibonanga simo\x + 4.33,36.\x*; ilizwi kuphela\x + Eks. 20.22. 1 Kho. 19.12.\x*.
\v 13 Yamemezela kini isivumelwano sayo, eyalilaya ukuthi lisenze\x + 9.9,11.\x*, imilayo elitshumi\x + Eks. 34.28.\x*; njalo yayibhala ezibhebheni zamatshe ezimbili\x + Eks. 24.12.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli baxwayiswa ukuthi bangoni
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasingilaya ngalesosikhathi ukuthi ngilifundise izimiso lezahlulelo\x + Eks. 21.1-23.33.\x*, ukuze lizenze elizweni elidlulela kulo ukudla ilifa lalo.
\v 15 Ngakho-ke qaphelani kakhulu\x + Josh. 23.11.\x* ngenxa yemiphefumulo yenu\x + Josh. 23.11.\x*. Ngoba kalibonanga lasimo ngosuku iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhuluma kini eHorebe iphakathi komlilo\x + 4.12.\x*,
\v 16 hlezi lizone, lizenzele isithombe esibaziweyo\x + Eks. 20.4. Dute. 4.23. 5.8.\x*, isimo saloba yiwuphi umfanekiso\x + 2 Lan. 33.7,15. Hez. 8.3.5.\x*, isifanekiso sowesilisa loba sowesifazana\x + Josh. 22.28; Hez. 8.3; Roma 1.23.\x*,
\v 17 isifanekiso saloba yiyiphi inyamazana esemhlabeni\x + Josh. 22.28; Hez. 8.3; Roma 1.23.\x*, isifanekiso saloba yiyiphi inyoni elempiko ephapha emazulwini\x + Josh. 22.28; Hez. 8.3; Roma 1.23.\x*,
\v 18 isifanekiso saloba yikuphi okuhuquzelayo emhlabeni\x + Josh. 22.28; Hez. 8.3; Roma 1.23.\x*, isifanekiso saloba yiyiphi inhlanzi esemanzini ngaphansi komhlaba\x + Josh. 22.28; Hez. 8.3; Roma 1.23.\x*.
\v 19 Futhi hlezi uphakamisele amehlo akho emazulwini, lapho ubona ilanga lenyanga lezinkanyezi\x + 17.3. Jobe 31.26,27.\x*, ibutho lonke lamazulu\x + Gen. 2.1. 2 Kho. 17.16. 21.3.\x*, uyengwe, ukukhothamele, ukukhonze\x + 30.17.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekwabele izizwe zonke ngaphansi kwamazulu wonke.
\v 20 Kodwa lina iN\nd kosi\nd* yalithatha, yalikhupha esithandweni sensimbi, eGibhithe\x + 1 Kho. 8.51. Jer. 11.4.\x*, ukuze libe kuyo ngabantu belifa, njengalamuhla\x + 9.29. 32.9.\x*.
\v 21 Futhi iN\nd kosi\nd* yangithukuthelela ngenxa yenu, yafunga ukuthi kangiyikuchapha iJordani, lokuthi kangiyikungena kulelolizwe elihle iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona libe yilifa\x + 1.37.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngizafela kulelilizwe\x + 2 Pet. 1.13-15.\x*, ngingachaphi iJordani\x + 3.27.\x*; kodwa lina lizachapha, lidle ilifa lalelolizwe elihle\x + 3.25.\x*.
\v 23 Ziqapheleni\x + 4.9.\x* hlezi likhohlwe isivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu eyasenza lani\x + 4.9.\x*, lizenzele isithombe esibaziweyo, umfanekiso waloba yikuphi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekwenqabele khona.
\v 24 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ingumlilo oqothulayo\x + Eks. 24.17. Dute. 9.3. Heb. 12.29.\x*, uNkulunkulu olobukhwele\x + Eks. 20.5. Isa. 42.8.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Lapho uzala abantwana labantwana babantwana, njalo selihlale elizweni isikhathi eside, uba lisonakala, lenze isithombe esibaziweyo, umfanekiso waloba yikuphi\x + 4.16. Eks. 32.7.\x*, lenze okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 9.18. 2 Kho. 17.17.\x* ukuze liyithukuthelise\x + 9.18. 2 Kho. 17.17.\x*,
\v 26 ngibiza amazulu lomhlaba lamuhla ukuze kufakaze kumelene lani ukuthi lizabhubha lokubhubha masinyane lisuka elizweni elichapha iJordani ukuya kilo ukuze libe yilifa lenu; kaliyikwelula insuku zenu phezu kwalo, ngoba lizabhujiswa lokubhujiswa\x + 30.18,19. 31.28. 8.19. 32.1. Hlab. 50.4. Isa. 1.2. Jer. 2.12. 6.19. Mika 6.2.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* izalichithachitha phakathi kwezizwe\x + Levi 26.33.\x*, lisale libalutshwana ngenani phakathi kwezizwe, lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ezalixotshela khona\x + Gen. 34.30.\x*.
\v 28 Lapho lizakhonza onkulunkulu, umsebenzi wezandla zabantu, izigodo lamatshe\x + 28.36,64. Jer. 16.13.\x*, abangaboniyo, abangezwayo, abangadliyo, labanganukiyo\x + Hlab. 115.4-6. 135.15-17. Isa. 44.9. 46.7.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa lilapho liyidinge iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, uzayithola uba uyidinga ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke\x + 2 Lan. 15.4. Jer. 29.13,14. Levi 26.39-42. Dute. 30.1-3. Neh. 1.9. Isa. 55.6,7.\x*.
\v 30 Lapho usekuhluphekeni, lezizinto zonke zikwehlela, ekupheleni kwezinsuku\x + 31.29. Hos. 3.5. Gen. 49.1.\x*, uzaphendukela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, ulalele ilizwi layo\x + Jow. 2.12.\x*;
\v 31 ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho inguNkulunkulu olomusa, kayiyikukutshiya, kayiyikukubhubhisa, kayiyikukhohlwa isivumelwano saboyihlo, eyasifunga kubo\x + Eks. 34.6. 2 Lan. 30.9. Neh. 9.31. Jona 4.2.\x*.
\v 32 Ngoba buza-ke ngensuku zamandulo ezazingaphambi kwakho, kusukela osukwini uNkulunkulu adala ngalo umuntu emhlabeni\x + Jobe 8.8. 32.7.\x*, kusukela komunye umkhawulo wamazulu kuze kube komunye umkhawulo wamazulu, ukuthi kwake kwaba khona yini \add into enje\add* njengale into enkulu, kumbe kwezwakala enjengayo yini\x + Mat. 24.31. Mark. 13.27.\x*?
\v 33 Abantu \add bake\add* bezwa yini ilizwi likaNkulunkulu likhuluma livela phakathi komlilo, njengalokhu ulizwile wena, waphila\x + Eks. 24.11. Dute. 5.24,26. Eks. 33.20.\x*?
\v 34 Futhi uNkulunkulu \add wake\add* wazama yini ukuyazithathela isizwe phakathi kwesizwe, ngezilingo\x + 7.19. 29.3.\x*, ngezibonakaliso\x + Eks. 7.3. Dute. 26.8. Jer. 32.21.\x*, langezimangaliso\x + Eks. 7.3. Dute. 26.8. Jer. 32.21.\x*, langempi, langesandla esilamandla\x + Eks. 3.19. 13.9. Dute. 6.21. 7.8. 26.8. 34.12. Jer. 32.21.\x*, langengalo eyeluliweyo\x + Eks. 6.6. Dute. 26.8. Jer. 32.21.\x*, langezesabiso ezinkulu\x + 26.8. 34.12. Jer. 32.21.\x*, njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu eyalenzela khona eGibhithe phambi kwamehlo akho?
\v 35 Wena wakutshengiswa, ukuze wazi ukuthi uJehova unguNkulunkulu; kakho omunye ngaphandle kwakhe\x + 1 Sam. 2.2. Dute. 4.39. 32.39. 2 Sam. 22.32. Isa. 45.5,18,22. Mark. 12.32.\x*.
\v 36 Esemazulwini wakuzwisa ilizwi lakhe ukukufundisa; lemhlabeni wakutshengisa umlilo wakhe omkhulu, lamazwi akhe wawezwa evela phakathi komlilo\x + Eks. 19.9,19. 20.18,22.\x*.
\v 37 Njalo ngoba wabathanda oyihlo, wakhetha inzalo yabo emva kwabo, wakukhupha eGibhithe ebusweni bakhe ngamandla akhe amakhulu\x + 10.15.\x*,
\v 38 ukuxotsha elifeni izizwe ezinkulu lezilamandla kulawe phambi kwakho, ukukungenisa, ukukupha ilizwe lazo, libe yilifa, njengalamuhla\x + Eks. 15.9; 7.1; 9.1,4,5.\x*.
\v 39 Ngakho yazi lamuhla, ukukhumbule enhliziyweni yakho ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu emazulwini phezulu, lemhlabeni phansi\x + Josh. 2.11.\x*; kakho omunye\x + 4.35.\x*.
\v 40 Ngakho uzagcina izimiso zakhe lemilayo yakhe engikulaya yona lamuhla\x + Levi 22.31.\x*, ukuze kukulungele labantwana bakho emva kwakho, lokuze welule izinsuku phezu kwelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona, zonke izinsuku\x + 22.7; 5.16,29,33. 6.2,3,18. 11.9. 12.25,28. Zaga 10.27.\x*.
\s Ukukhethwa kwemizi emithathu yokuphephela
\p
\v 41 Khona uMozisi wehlukanisa imizi emithathu nganeno kweJordani ngasempumalanga\x + Nani 35.6,14.\x*,
\v 42 ukuthi abalekele kuyo umbulali obulele umakhelwane wakhe kungeyisikho ngabomo\x + 19.4.\x*, obengamzondi mandulo, ukuze abalekele komunye waleyomizi aphile\x + Gen. 31.2. Dute. 19.4.\x*;
\v 43 iBezeri enkangala\x + Josh. 20.8.\x* elizweni lamagceke, elabakoRubeni\x + 3.10.\x*; leRamothi eGileyadi, elabakoGadi; leGolani eBashani, elabakoManase.
\p
\v 44 Njalo yilo umlayo uMozisi awubeka phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 45 Lobu yibufakazi lezimiso lezahlulelo uMozisi akukhuluma ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli ekuphumeni kwabo eGibhithe,
\v 46 nganeno kweJordani, esigodini maqondana leBeti-Peyori, elizweni likaSihoni inkosi yamaAmori\x + 3.29. Josh. 13.20.\x*, owayehlala eHeshiboni, uMozisi labantwana bakoIsrayeli abamtshayayo ekuphumeni kwabo eGibhithe\x + Nani 21.24. Dute. 1.4.\x*.
\v 47 Basebesidla ilifa lelizwe lakhe lelizwe likaOgi inkosi yeBashani, amakhosi amabili amaAmori, ayenganeno kweJordani ngasempumalanga\x + Nani 21.33,35. Dute. 3.3,4.\x*,
\v 48 kusukela eAroweri esekhunjini lwesifula seArinoni\x + 2.36.\x*, kuze kufike entabeni yeSiyoni\x + 3.9.\x*, eyiHermoni\x + 3.9.\x*,
\v 49 lamagceke wonke nganeno kweJordani ngasempumalanga, kuze kube selwandle lwamagceke\x + 3.9.\x*, ngaphansi kweAshidodi-Pisiga\x + 3.17.\x*.